Project Title

Streetwear Website

Description

This is a responsive website developed as part of a web development assignment. The website showcases a streetwear brand and includes features such as product display, user registration, login system, and basic navigation between pages.

The purpose of this project is to demonstrate skills in:

HTML, CSS, JavaScript
PHP
Form handling and validation
Database connectivity 

 Features
Home page with brand introduction
Product/gallery page displaying items
User registration system
User login system
Admin approval 
Responsive design for mobile and desktop
Contact page 

 Technologies Used
HTML5
CSS
JavaScript
PHP
MySQL 
XAMPP / WAMP 

